OL,6,FShe's become known for a number of
OL,7,Fviral moments, including when she said
OL,8,Fthe naughtiest thing she ever did was
OL,9,F"run through fields of wheat", and
OL,10,Fsome slightly awkward dance moves.
OL,12,FBut her time as prime minister was
OL,13,Falso dominated by desperate attempts
OL,14,Fto deliver among Tory infighting, and
OL,15,Fthe controversial "hostile
OL,16,Fenvironment" policy she brought in
OL,17,Fwhen she was home secretary.
OL,19,FHere's a rundown of the key moments in
OL,20,Fthe former prime minister's career:
