OL,6,FWhen Mrs May became prime minister in
OL,7,F2016, she took over from David Cameron
OL,8,Fwho stepped down after Britain voted
OL,9,Fto leave the EU, despite campaigning
OL,10,Fto remain.
OL,12,FThe challenge for Theresa May was then
OL,13,Fto deliver a Brexit deal that would
OL,14,Fsatisfy both sides of the divided Tory
OL,15,Fparty.
OL,17,FShe was close to succeeding in 2018,
OL,18,Fafter the Cabinet supported her deal
OL,19,Fthat would give Britain continued
OL,20,Faccess to the single market for for
OL,21,Fgoods.
