OL,7,Fher Brexit Secretary David Davis when
OL,8,Fhe resigned, and his resignation was
OL,9,Ffollowed by that of Boris Johnson, her
OL,10,Fthen foreign secretary.
OL,12,FIn December 2018 MPs launched a vote
OL,13,Fof no confidence against her, which
OL,14,Fshe won.
OL,16,FBut opposition to her leadership
OL,17,Fremained strong, and .
