OL,6,F'Hostile environment' and the Windrush
OL,7,Fscandal
OL,9,FMrs May was home secretary from 2010
OL,10,Fto 2016, and became defined by the
OL,12,FShe told the Telegraph her aim was "to
OL,13,Fcreate here in Britain a really
OL,14,Fhostile environment for illegal
OL,15,Fmigration".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/17
