OL,6,FThe hostile environment policy also
OL,7,Fled to the Windrush scandal, where
OL,8,Fhundreds of Caribbean people living in
OL,9,Fthe UK were wrongly detained, denied
OL,10,Flegal rights, and threatened with
OL,11,Fdeportation.
OL,13,FThe describes people who arrived in
OL,14,FBritain between from the Caribbean
OL,15,Fbetween 1948 and 1971.
