OL,7,Fterm "hostile environment" in her
OL,8,Fmemoir released last year saying "it
OL,9,Fwas not a good term to use", and
OL,10,Fblamed the Labour prime minister
OL,11,Fduring the time the Windrush
OL,12,Fgeneration arrived for failing to give
OL,13,Farrivals paperwork to prove their
OL,14,Fright to be here.
