OL,6,FShe was criticised for her response to
OL,7,Fthe tragedy, as she failed to meet the
OL,8,Fsurvivors of the blaze.
OL,10,FIn 2018 she said she will "always
OL,11,Fregret" her immediate response,
OL,12,Fwriting in the Evening Standard that:
OL,13,F"What I did not do on that first visit
OL,14,Fwas meet the residents and survivors
OL,15,Fwho had escaped the blaze.
OL,17,F"But the residents of Grenfell Tower
OL,18,Fneeded to know that those in power
OL,19,Frecognised and understood their
OL,20,Fdespair.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/17
