OL,6,F"And I will always regret that by not
OL,7,Fmeeting them that day, it seemed as
OL,8,Fthough I didn't care", she said.
OL,10,FShe was then labelled "disgraceful" by
OL,11,Fthe firefighters' union for listing
OL,12,Fher response to Grenfell as a proud
OL,13,Fpart of her legacy in her resignation
OL,14,Fspeech.
OL,16,FMatt Wrack of the Fire Brigade's Union
OL,17,Fsaid she had delayed the inquiry, and
OL,18,F"kicked scrutiny of corporate and
OL,19,Fgovernment interests into the long-
OL,20,Fgrass".
