OL,6,FFunny moments
OL,8,FThe former prime minister is also
OL,9,Fknown for a number of awkward moments
OL,10,Fthat went viral.
OL,12,FThey include when she told ITV's
OL,13,FTonight programme the naughtiest thing
OL,14,Fshe ever did was "run through fields
OL,15,Fof wheat" as a child.
OL,17,FShe was then widely mocked for a clip
OL,18,Fof her dancing with school children
OL,19,Fduring a visit to South Africa then
OL,20,Fwent viral in 2018.
